high_descs: turn right and walk forwards to the sink, then take a right and walk forwards to the kitchen counter and stove
grab the tea kettle off of the kitchen counter in the corner of the kitchen counter's
turn around and walk over to the sink on the right just up ahead
place the tea kettle inside of the sink and clean it off
turn right and walk over to the front of the stove ahead on the right
place the tea kettle inside of the cabinet to the bottom left of the stove
anns.task_desc: place a clean tea kettle inside of the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and move to the left side of the stove.
Pick up the teapot on the left side of the paper towels.
Turn around to your left and head to the sink.
Place the teapot in the sink and clean it off, remove it after you shut the water off.
Turn turn around and go to the bottom cabinet on the left side of the stove.
Place the teapot in the bottom cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Clean the teapot and put it into the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink then turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the tea pot to the left of the paper towels to your left.
Turn left and take as step to your left to face the sink.
Fill the kettle with water in the sink then shut off the tap and pick it back up.
Turn right and take a step to your right.
Open the cupboard to the left of the stove and put the kettle down there.
anns.task_desc: Put a kettle of water in the cupboard.
